{
  "stem": "16792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 281.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When I came to-- when I came down in the mine, I ask which pays the most money, and he said the most money pays [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means you couldn't go in like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "You must go in on the roller.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "You have a roller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "You lay on the back, and you roll in, and then you chip the-- you put a mask.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "You have a mask, and then you chip to coal, and the coal was going out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this they pay the most money, and I was working down there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made a lot of money, OK?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russian ruble was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was working down there many months, and my friend, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Lipe ?] Klappholtz, also was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he was working, he don't want to go to this job because this is the toughest job what it is, and he was going to make streets in the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's several hundred feet deep, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And make streets with dynamite and things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was-- at one time, he was making a street not far from me, 20 feet or something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had something when I was knocking and I was moving out a little bit, I wanted to take a little bit more air, I had something-- something I had which is not normally when they blow up the street.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I roll out, and I see that the whole thing is-- you don't see any people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You only see stones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They covered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I call a couple more people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took off the stones, and my-- my friend was unconscious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was got a-- got a broken leg, and they took him to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
